               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t17850223-20-cd107" type="crimeDate">21st of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850223-20-off106 t17850223-20-cd107"></join> last, one mare, price 30 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17850223-20-victim375" type="victimName">
                     Jacob 
                     Cave
                  <interp inst="t17850223-20-victim375" type="surname" value="Cave"></interp>
